            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Of our triumphant King!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s coming for the churches"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Where His sweet praises ring."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Come, Lord, come reap the firstfruits,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As draws the harvest nigh,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And to Thy throne do take us,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
